VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'you\'re paying per token or, you know, managing your session limit. Okay, so what is Printing Press? What are we looking at today? So if you go to printingpress.dev, this is what it will look like. It\'s a very new tool just dropped like yesterday and I\'ve been playing with it all day today. And I\'ve'

